OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FFurther
OL,6,Frain, sleet and snow, heavy at times
OL,7,Fthis evening, and strong to gale force
OL,8,Fnortherly winds, severe around coasts.
OL,9,FWinds easing and turning showery
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FOften cloudy with frequent
OL,13,Fblustery showers from the west, heavy
OL,14,Fand wintry at times. Some bright
OL,15,Fspells developing between showers at
OL,16,Ftimes.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
