OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry on Monday, some sunshine but
OL,7,Fclouding over, patchy rain for Isles.
OL,8,FSunny start Tuesday, then rain
OL,9,Freaching west later, some heavy.
OL,10,FOccasional rain or showers on
OL,11,FWednesday.
